title: Pink Edition Rock Model 5 A with 16GB RAM Now Available for ~$109.50
description: Arace Tech has recently showcased the Radxa Rock Model 5 A in an eye-catching pink edition, notable for its competitive pricing. This model boasts up to 16GB of RAM and incorporates PCIe2, enhancing its storage capabilities. Furthermore, it now supports the  lightweight operating system DietPi.
